{
  "texts": [
    "• MAP@10 (mean average precision) computes the average precision at each rank position where a gold passage is retrieved, and then averages this over all queries.",
    "We truncate at rank 10.",
    "• MRR@10 (mean reciprocal rank) computes the mean of the reciprocal rank of the first correct passage, rewarding systems that surface a gold document as early as possible.",
    "We also truncate at rank 10.",
    "For HotpotQA, we adopt the official QA-centric evaluation metrics introduced in the original benchmark (Yang et al., 2018; Rajpurkar et al., 2016)."
  ]
}